<h2 id="toc4"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Welcome to “Unregistered Scpcrnp&quot;</span></span></h2>
<p>I've gotten in the <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">bad</span> <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">good</span> habit of username jumping. This page will act as an unofficial author page for the various names until I re-approach some permanence. Below is an accumulation of articles I've written since leaving the site as scpcrnp. Articles are grouped in chronological order by usernames.</p>
</div>
<div class="content-panel standalone series" style="background: url(http://themes.wdfiles.com/local--files/foundationmedical/smoothwrapper2a);">
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><a href="https://www.deviantart.com/nicholai1806/art/Bahamut-FFX-110365988"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scpcrnp-s-author-page/bahamuticon.png" width="55px" alt="bahamuticon.png" class="image" /></a><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-9')">9</a></sup></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:105%;"><span style="color: #006abf"><span class="math-inline">$-Mnml-$</span></span></span></p>
